		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">United States presidential line of succession</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>The <b>United States presidential line of succession</b> defines who may become or act as <a href="/wiki/President_of_the_United_States" title="President of the United States">President of the United States</a> upon the incapacity, death, resignation, or removal from office (by <a href="/wiki/Impeachment" title="Impeachment">impeachment</a> and subsequent conviction) of a sitting president or a <a href="/wiki/President-elect_of_the_United_States" title="President-elect of the United States">president-elect</a>.</p>
