<p><a name="Current_order" id="Current_order"></a></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline">Current order</span></h2>
<p>This is a list of the current presidential <a href="/wiki/Line_of_succession" title="Line of succession" class="mw-redirect">line of succession</a><sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup>, as specified by the <a href="/wiki/Presidential_Succession_Act_of_1947" title="Presidential Succession Act of 1947" class="mw-redirect">Presidential Succession Act of 1947</a> (<a href="/wiki/Title_3_of_the_United_States_Code" title="Title 3 of the United States Code">3 U.S.C.</a>&#160;<a href="http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/3/19.html" class="external text" title="http://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/3/19.html" rel="nofollow">§&#160;19</a>) and subsequent amendments to include newly created cabinet officers.</p>
